channel.title: Price check for all my gamecube and x-box games, please
channel.description:
I have these games to sell, and I need individual prices/guildelines in which to sell them. I have 17 games to sell. (BTW) If you've never played/heard of the game, don't give me a price check.
X-Box _____________ Fable- UFC Tapout 2- Scooby Doo Night of 100 frights- Halo 1- 007 agent under fire- Fight Club- Harry Potter and the chamber of secrets- NFL 2k3 (2003)-
Gamecube ____________ Spongebob battle for bikini bottom- Super smash brothers melee- Luigi's mansion- Jimmy neutron jet fusion- Nascar Thunder 2003- Defender- YU-GI-OH The falsebound kingdom- Zelda and the Twilight princess (mint conditon)- Zelda and the wind waker-
If someone can post some prices, id appreciate it. im trying to save up for something. thank you!
